                     </li>
                     
                     <li><a href="../apparatuses/her_voice_has_ceased_to_joy_apparatus.php#JRHERVOICEHASCEASED" target="_blank" class="inactive"><span class="title-poem-JRHERVOICEHASCEASED">&#x201C;Her voice has ceased to joy, her look to bless&#x201D;</span></a> (p. 108v).
